Given script help you to host a static website using S3 and display "Hellow World" from your local using a windows command script
Download the Zip code to your local and extract the files
create a Test Folder in your local and copy Policy.Json file to it and note the file path. This path needs to be upated in the S3.cmd script
Update S3.cmd with your AWs secure access key ID and Secret access key, Region,Policy.Json file copied path and bucket name  in the script and save.
Make sure you have installed AWS CLI if not refer to this link  https://docs.aws.amazon.com/cli/latest/userguide/install-cliv2-windows.html
Run the script by double clicking on it
To Test the website which is hosted using S3 Use this URLafter updating the bucket name and region and paste in your browser. URL is https://<Buketname>.s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/index.html
